<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="659" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="16.[131,775,1165,1348]" pageId="16" pageNumber="659">ETYMOLOGY. — This wasp is dedicated to Alice Cibois, to honour her dedication as president of the Swiss Systematics Society and her creative and innovative efforts to promote our craft among the general public. She especially drew attention to the ongoing discovery and naming of new species through the curated list “New Species Swiss Made”, which year after year feature dozens to hundred new species across the tree of life.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
